The version you apply patch doesn't really matter - your patch is just not cracked so if you apply it to any version you will get error.

The game crashes after the "burn em out" mission is due to corruption in the movie file "pel1b_load.bik", thus, make it impossible to start "Relentless" mission.
Though the file is watchable using rad video player, but the game cannot play it. So the solution here is using another bik video file and rename it to "pel1b_load.bik".
@ryzy: If you don't mind, please upload pel1b_load.bik else where. It's in main/video folder.
